## Marriage  

He married Margaret, daughter of [Sir James Halyburton](/Sir_James_Halyburton) of Pitcur manor, [Kettins](/Kettins), on 15 November 1595. They had three children: &#91;5&#93;  

* Sir Peter Hay (died [decessit vita patris](/Decessit_vita_patris) at Kinfauns, 1621), unmarried  
* [George Hay](/George_Hay,_2nd_Earl_of_Kinnoull) (d. 1644)  
* Lady Margaret, married to [Alexander Lindsay, 2nd Lord Spynie](/Alexander_Lindsay,_2nd_Lord_Spynie)  

